reviews.name: Hydroxycut Lean Protein Milk Chocolate Protein Shakes, 11 fl oz, 4 count
reviews.reviewText: They are great for on the run moms. I drink 2 a day for the last or or so weeks and I have lost 9 pounds. I still eat, but I do these also and just eat a lot less. I love them. Very disappointed that I can not find them. I am almost out and I am afraid I will start to eat more again. Can not find the bars at Walmart either. They are always sold out of shakes and bars :(
reviews.title: Love these Very disappointed that I cant find them

reviews.name: Hydroxycut Lean Protein Milk Chocolate Protein Shakes, 11 fl oz, 4 count
reviews.reviewText: OMG!!! If you love chocolate, you'll love these!!! It actually tastes like a rich & creamy milk shake without the calories!!! The shake also fills the chocolate craving that one might get from time to time! I'll definitely invest in more and the cost is GREAT!!! Thanks Walmart!
reviews.title: Nice & rich!!!

reviews.name: Hydroxycut Lean Protein Milk Chocolate Protein Shakes, 11 fl oz, 4 count
reviews.reviewText: The best shakes I've ever had, and Walmart either discontinued them or something… I am so angry… Ive been out of them for a month… I would drink 2 a day before. If these don't come back soon I'm seriously boycotting.
reviews.title: Very Angry

reviews.name: Hydroxycut Lean Protein Milk Chocolate Protein Shakes, 11 fl oz, 4 count
reviews.reviewText: I got these the other day and I was unexpectadly amazed!!! They taste great and have 16g of protein and no sugar!!! It feels like I am cheating every time I grab one!!! I love them because they are portable, taste amazing and get satisfy my cravings for chocolate!!!
reviews.title: Delicious and Satisfying!!!!
